---
title: Sweet Potato Risotto with Brazil Nut Drizzle and Pancetta
description: Our velvety sweet potato and pancetta risotto is full of fresh flavours perfect for a Summer evening. To take flavours to the next level, Chef Mimi has topped it with a Brazil nut drizzle which will give a lovely crunchy texture to this deliciously creamy dish. If you’ve got fussy eaters at the table, just leave this last step out and serve up!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sweet-potato-risotto-304c5dc8-9e8c2d27.jpg
